@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<main>
    <section class="row" aria-labelledby="aspnetTitle">
        <h1 id="title" class="text-center">Programing Hero</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center">Choose from a wide range of industry-standard courses designed to take you from a complete beginner to a professional developer.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
        <section class="col-md-3 bg-success rounded-2 m-2 p-3 text-bg-success" aria-labelledby="gettingStartedTitle">
            <h2 id="gettingStartedTitle"> Project-Based Learning Approach</h2>
            <p>
                Our curriculum is designed to move beyond theory and focus on real-world application.
                You will build professional-grade projects from scratch, helping you understand how code works in a practical environment.
                This hands-on experience ensures that you are ready to tackle complex challenges in the industry.
            </p>

        </section>
        <section class="col-md-3 bg-success rounded-2 m-2 p-3 text-bg-success" aria-labelledby="librariesTitle">
            <h2 id="librariesTitle"> Personalized Mentorship & Support</h2>
            <p>
                We believe no student should feel stuck while learning to code.
                Our dedicated mentors provide one-on-one support to clear your doubts and guide you through difficult concepts.
                This constant encouragement helps you stay motivated and ensures a smooth learning journey from start to finish.
            </p>

        </section>
        <section class="col-md-3 bg-success rounded-2 m-2 p-3 text-bg-success" aria-labelledby="hostingTitle">
            <h2 id="hostingTitle"> Career Success & Job Placement</h2>
            <p>
                Our ultimate goal is to see you succeed in your professional life. We provide intensive career grooming, including resume building, mock interviews,
                and direct connections with top tech companies. We don't just teach you how to code; we help you launch a rewarding career in the tech world.
            </p>
        </section>

    </div>

    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
        <section class="col-md-4 bg-success rounded-2 m-2 p-3 text-bg-success" aria-labelledby="gettingStartedTitle">
            <h2 id="gettingStartedTitle"> Join a Global Tribe of Future-Proof Developers</h2>
            <p>
                Learning to code shouldn't be a lonely journey. When you join our course, you aren’t just a student—you’re part of a thriving ecosystem. Gain access to exclusive Discord channels, 
                participate in weekend hackathons, and collaborate with peers on real-time coding challenges. Our community is where networking happens, ideas are born, 
                and lifelong professional partnerships are forged. Together, we code better.
            </p>

        </section>
        <section class="col-md-4 bg-success rounded-2 m-2 p-3 text-bg-success" aria-labelledby="librariesTitle">
            <h2 id="librariesTitle"> The Fast-Track to Web Development</h2>
            <p>
                Why spend years in a classroom when you can master the most in-demand skills in weeks? We’ve trimmed the fluff and focused on the "must-know" technologies that modern companies actually use.
                Our curriculum is optimized for speed without sacrificing depth, allowing you to transition from a beginner to a job-ready developer in record time.
                Stop wasting time on outdated theories and start building what matters.
            </p>

        </section>
        <section class="col-md-4 bg-success rounded-2 m-2 p-3 text-bg-success" aria-labelledby="hostingTitle">
            <h2 id="hostingTitle"> Master the Tools the Pros Use</h2>
            <p>
                Knowing how to write a loop is only half the battle. To succeed in tech, you need to work like a professional. Our course dives deep into the industry-standard "Developer Workflow"—including Git version control,
                GitHub collaboration, debugging like a pro, and deploying your apps to the cloud. You won't just learn a programming language;
                you’ll learn the entire lifecycle of software development so you can hit the ground running on day one of your new job.
            </p>
        </section>

    </div>
</main>